Requirements:
Users can browse movies
Users can browse theaters
Users can see available seats for a show
Users can select multiple seats
Seat locking,When user selects seats,they should become temporarily unavailable.
Payment
Booking confirmation
Cancellation, release seats


Non functional Requirements
No double booking ****
Fast seat availability lookup
Atomic booking, either all selected booked or none ,never partial
Extensible code



